GORMLEYESQUE tracked two wide and between horses, shifted four wide at the three furlong pole, then faded. BRISBANE ROAD dueled for the lead two wide and weakened between horses in upper stretch. SHACKLED BY LUST was shuffled back behind DIVINE GRACE in the opening furlong, trailed around the turn, and was outrun.
